  <p>Creates a <link xref="GLib.DateTime"/> corresponding to this exact instant in the local
time zone.</p>  <p>This is equivalent to calling <link xref="GLib.DateTime.new_now"/> with the time
zone returned by <link xref="GLib.TimeZone.new_local"/>.</p>
  <p>Since 2.26</p>
